DISCLAIMER FOR AI-CONTROLLED SYSTEM OPERATIONS:

This software provides voice control over Windows system operations, including
but not limited to file deletion, system shutdown, and command execution.

USERS ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR:
- Reviewing all system-changing commands before confirming with the keyword
- Maintaining backups of critical data
- Understanding the risks of automated system control
- Setting appropriate access controls

